---
title: Barbecue Pulled Pork Flatbreads with Tomato and Mozzarella Cheese
description: Your backyard cookout just met pizza night—*worlds collide*. The crispy flatbread crust in this dish is loaded with barbecue favorites like ready-to-heat pulled pork and a smoky sauce, then given an Italian accent via mozzarella cheese and tomato. In other words, it’s both lick-your-lips, stick-to-your-fingers good as well as a piping hot piece of pie perfection.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/barbecue-pulled-pork-flatbreads-212afd19.jpg
